snippet.title: How I Lost 50 Pounds Waist Training !! | Amber Myriah
snippet.description:
Hey ! In this video I share how I use a waist clincher/ waist training to help lose belly fat/weight. In addition with the clincher I also eat clean (except for cheat days lol) & do light work outs. Hopefully This video helps anybody else out there who is interested in waist training & wants to lose a few inches off the waist.
